      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-02773'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040427_GCR_170' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 21 [<span class="italic">Intervention orders</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0660P0-02774'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040427_GCR_171' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
